OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales 'stretched too
OL,4,Cthin' to deal with pollution incidents
OL,6,FThere is "grave concern" over Natural
OL,7,FResources Wales' (NRW) decision to
OL,8,Freduce the number of low category
OL,9,Fpollution incidents it responds to,
OL,10,Faccording to a Senedd committee.
OL,12,FThe Climate Change, Environment and
OL,13,FInfrastructure Committee heard
OL,14,Fevidence from the watchdog as part of
OL,15,Fan annual review.
OL,17,FAs part of the evidence, the committee
OL,18,Fquestioned NRW bosses over "water,
OL,19,Fwaste, industry and responding to
OL,20,Fpollution incidents".
