OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales 'stretched too
OL,4,Cthin' to deal with pollution incidents
OL,6,FThe report concluded the watchdog's
OL,7,Fability to respond to pollution
OL,8,Fincidents is "concerning", adding, "it
OL,9,Fremains unclear what the impact will
OL,10,Fbe of the inevitable lack of
OL,11,Fenforcement."
OL,13,FFunding is blamed for the lack of
OL,14,Fenforcement of water quality and
OL,15,Fpollution incidents, with the cross-
OL,16,Fparty committee concluding that
OL,17,FNatural Resources Wales is "not funded
OL,18,Fsufficiently to deal with its
OL,19,Fmultitude of functions, duties, and
OL,20,Fresponsibilities.
