OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales 'stretched too
OL,4,Cthin' to deal with pollution incidents
OL,6,F"Years of underinvestment have
OL,7,Fstretched NRW too thin."
OL,9,FLast year, a report, shared
OL,10,Fexclusively with ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,11,Fshows a substantial increase in the
OL,12,Famount of funding needed as nature and
OL,13,Fspecies struggle to survive in our
OL,14,Fconstantly evolving climate.
OL,16,FCeri Davies, Interim Chief Executive
OL,17,Fat Natural Resources Wales, said, "We
OL,18,Ftake our responsibilities for
OL,19,Fprotecting the environment very
OL,20,Fseriously.
