OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales 'stretched too
OL,4,Cthin' to deal with pollution incidents
OL,6,F"Responding to environmental incidents
OL,7,Fis a core part of our work, especially
OL,8,Fas climate, nature, and pollution
OL,9,Fpressures accelerate, and the number
OL,10,Fof incidents reported to us increases.
OL,11,FLike all public bodies with finite
OL,12,Fresources, we must focus our efforts
OL,13,Fwhere we can make the greatest impact.
OL,15,F"We will always prioritise incidents
OL,16,Fthat pose the highest risk to people
OL,17,Fand nature, putting people on the
OL,18,Fground if needed, and ensuring a
OL,19,Fresponse that is risk-based,
OL,20,Fintelligence-led, and data-driven.
