OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales 'stretched too
OL,4,Cthin' to deal with pollution incidents
OL,6,F"Our corporate plan to 2030 also
OL,7,Fcommits us to minimising pollution
OL,8,Fthrough more effective prevention and
OL,9,Fresponse. A key part of this work
OL,10,Finvolves enhancing the way we assess
OL,11,Fand respond to environmental incidents.
OL,13,F"Most incidents reported to us are low-
OL,14,Flevel, often with little or no
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact."
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government said, "We thank
OL,18,Fthe committee for its report and will
OL,19,Fconsider its recommendations
OL,20,Fcarefully."
